## Additional Terms for NotebookLM MCP Server

This project provides automation tools for Google NotebookLM through the Model Context Protocol (MCP).

**Author**: Kangkhengyun (khengyun)
**Institution**: FPT University, Vietnam
**ORCID**: 0000-0003-3616-0367

